creator: B.F.
descriptionHtml:
On a sleepless night, get a peaceful time with cozy campfire.
Make your favorite ASMR combinations.

Gather firewood and make a campfire.
Use firewood to make a campfire and collect warmth.
Buy various playable sound items such as rain sound, frying sound, boiling sound etc.
Combine those items and make your own ASMR world.

When you go to bed,
When you need cozy atmosphere,
Enjoy the atmosphere with your own created ASMR world.



~How to play~

- Every map has objects that act as a tree and a fire.
- Tab tree to gather firewood, and tab fire to maintain it.
- Firewood is used as a fuel and also an upgrade material.
- Warmth will be collected during the fire is on(1 warmth every 5~15sec).
- High fule amount boosts warmth collecting speed.
- Fire Warmth also will be collected when you're leaving the game(but the minimum speed).
- Warmth can be used to purchase and use various ASMR sound items.



~Main Updates~

1.0.x
- Adding 'Night Forest Camping Place'.

1.1.x
- Adding 'Midsummer Korean Rural House'.
- Adding an item 'Piano' to the forest.
descriptionShort: Make your ASMR world with campfire.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Midsummer Korean Rural House added.
- Piano added to Night Forest.
- Harvesting delay for carrot and egg.
